        " قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلْوَصِيَّةُ تَمَامُ مَا نَقَصَ مِنَ اَلزَّكَاةِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5413 - Masadah ibn Sadaqah Al-Rabii narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), that Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"Making a will completes what is lacking from the payment of zakat.\""
        ]
